<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pure Produce</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/whyus.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/8f62f8789d.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100">
    <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>
    <%- include('./partials/flash') %>
    <div class="feat bg-gray pt-5 pb-5">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="section-head col-sm-12">
              <h4><span>Why Choose</span> Us?</h4>
              <p>At Pure Produce, we are dedicated to providing customers with the highest quality organic fruits and vegetables. We understand the importance of transparency, sustainability, and the health benefits associated with organic produce. Here's how we validate our commitment to organic practices:</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_one"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i></span>
                <h6>Direct Sourcing</h6>
                <p>We establish direct relationships with organic farmers who follow strict organic farming practices. We personally vet and select our suppliers to ensure that our products meet the highest organic standards.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_two"><i class="fa-solid fa-certificate"></i></span>
                <h6>Organic Certification</h6>
                <p>All the fruits and vegetables available on our website are sourced from certified organic farms. This certification ensures that our products are free from synthetic pesticides, GMOs, and harmful chemicals.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_three"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></span>
                <h6>Traceability and Transparency</h6>
                <p> We provide complete transparency regarding the origin of our products. Each product on our website includes information about farm & supplier, allowing customers to trace the journey of their products.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_four"><i class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-square-check"></i></span>
                <h6>Quality Assurance</h6>
                <p>We maintain strict quality control measures to ensure that only the freshest and highest quality products reaches our customers. Our team carefully inspects each item before it is dispatched for delivery.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_five"><i class="fa-solid fa-box"></i></span>
                <h6>Sustainable Packaging</h6>
                <p>We prioritize eco-friendly packaging materials for our organic fruits and vegetables. We use biodegradable or compostable packaging options whenever possible, minimizing our environmental impact.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
              <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_six"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck"></i></span>
                <h6>Delivery and Storage</h6>
                <p>We have invested in temperature-controlled storage facilities and refrigerated delivery vehicles to ensure that your products maintain their freshness and nutritional value during transit.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_seven"><i class="fa-solid fa-face-smile"></i></span>
                  <h6>Customer Feedback and Satisfaction</h6>
                  <p>We value our customers' feedback and continuously strive to improve our services. We encourage customers to share their feedback on our website. This helps us maintain the highest standards of quality and customer satisfaction.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                <div class="item"> <span class="icon feature_box_col_eight"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i></span>
                  <h6>Educational Resources</h6>
                  <p>We are committed to educating our customers about the benefits of organic farming and the importance of supporting sustainable agriculture. Our website provides resources to help customers make informed choices and understand the value of organic produce.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="section-head col-sm-12">
                <p>We are proud to offer a wide range of organic fruits and vegetables, cultivated with care and respect for the environment. By choosing Pure Produce, you can be confident in the authenticity and quality of the organic produce you receive.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>    
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
